==Nga ha Shayandima==
Shayandima ndi muḓi uno wanala tshipembe-vhukovhela ha [[Thohoyanḓou]]. Shayandima a si kule na Thohoyanḓou lune muthu anga tshimbila nga milenzhe. Ḓorobo khulwane dza tsini ndi [[Thohoyanḓou]], [[Sibasa]] na [[Louis Trichardt]].

==Pfunzo==
Gudedzi la Tshilidzini (Nursing College)li wanala henefha Shayandima. Gudedzi ili ndi la ugudisa vhathu mushumo wa vhunese. Gudedzi ili li wanala tsini na vhuongelo ha [[Tshilidzini]]. Shayandima huna zwikolo zwo vhambanaho zwine zwigudiswa vhagudiswa mabudo o vhambanaho. Tshikolo tsha Shayandima High tshofara thero dza Science na Mathametics, Khwevha yo fara thero dza Commercial ngeno dimani tsho fara thero dza vhulimisi. Tshilidzini Special School ndi tshikolo tshidzenaho vhaholevhali,tshikolo itshi ntshivha vhagudiswa pfudzo dza ntha vhukuma.

==Vhadzulapo==
Vhunzhi ha vhathu vha no dzula afha vha amba tshiVenḓa.

==Mishumo==
Ha-Ramasaga (Shayandima Industrial Site) ndi hune vhathu vhanzhi vha Shayandima vha shuma hone. Vhaṅwe vha vhathu vha Shayandima vha shuma Thohoyanḓou.

==Zwikolo / Schools==
Khala Shayandima, line la divheya nga lauri Shayandima Mavhoneni hu na zwikolo zwi tevhelaho.<br><br>

1. Lurenzheni Primary School<br>
2. Tshidumbi Junior Primary School<br>
3. Shayandima Secondary School<br>
4. Kwevha Commercial High School<br>
5. Dimani Agric High School<br>
6. School of Tomorrow (Christian School)<br><br>

Zwikolo izwi zwi na vhana vhanzhi vhonobva mashangoni atsini na a kule vha tshi tevhela yone pfunzo.

Kha vhothe vho dzhenaho Tshidumbi a huna a sa vha divhiho Vho-Mafumo(Thoho ya Tshikolo), Vho Nthai, Vhalaudzi(Maneer), Vho-Singo na vhanwevho. avha ndi vha dededzi vhe vha vha vha tshi divhea vhukuma nga mishumo yavho ya vhudi.
